summary: When you got appointed Thane of Falkreath somethimes housecarl Rayya dosnt spawn and are unable to gain as follower and Steward for your lakeview manor, This mod fixes that.
descriptionHtml:
When you got appointed Thane of Falkreath somethimes housecarl Rayya dosnt spawn and are unable to be gained as follower and Steward for your Lakeview manor, This mod fixes that.

She will spawn in Falkreath Jarls Longhouse

I really hope some will find this useful.

Install:

Download with Mannager or

Extract - cut - paste in skyrim Data folder.

If you like please Endorse =)

With best regards
Meyer189
